================
About the script
================

This script used create an application in nagios configuration.

------
How to
------

-a  use this option to specify the application name.
-d  use this option to specify the domain, if there is no domain, ignore it.
-s  use this option to specify the system, support multiple system.
-p specify the path of faurecia-nagios-configuration if you have more than one repo on your computer.Or you can ignore it, the script can find it automatic.

eg:
./create.py -a ijcore -d eit -s linux -s win -s aix -p /home/chengca/faurecia-nagios-configuration
